```class Solution {
    public boolean doesAliceWin(String s) {
        int n = s.length();
        int alice = 0, bob = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            if (s.charAt(i) == 'a' || s.charAt(i) == 'e' || s.charAt(i) == 'i' || s.charAt(i) == 'o' || s.charAt(i) == 'u') {
                if ((i & 1) == 0) bob++;
                else alice++;
            }
        }
        return alice > bob;
    }
}```
